      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup; boundary condition checklist completed.",
      "rationale": "Model setup independently reviewed by second analyst not involved in original construction. Boundary condition checklist (BC-CHK-F1717-v2) completed and signed. Material assignments verified against certified material test reports. Use error level 2 satisfied."
    },
    {
